<h2 id="Cookie">Cookie</h2>
<p>如果某个响应中包含一些cookie，可以快速访问它们，要想发送cookies到服务器，可以使用cookies参数</p>
<div class="code-container" data-rel="Python"><figure class="iseeu highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">url = urljoin(base,<span class="string">&#x27;/cookies&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">cookies = <span class="built_in">dict</span>(cookies_are=<span class="string">&#x27;working&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">r= requests.get(url,cookies=cookies)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(r.text)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<pre><code>&#123;
  &quot;cookies&quot;: &#123;
    &quot;cookies_are&quot;: &quot;working&quot;
  &#125;
&#125;
</code></pre>
<p>Cookie的返回对象为RequestCookieJar，它的行为和字典类似，但接口更为完整，适合跨域名跨路径使用。可以把CookieJar传到Requests中：</p>
